                              <decoNote xml:id="b1" type="bindingMaterial">
                                The book has a Modern European binding in <material key="cardboard">cardboard</material> boards, fully covered with brown <material
                                key="leather">leather</material>.
                              </decoNote>
                              <decoNote xml:id="b2" type="Boards">
                                  The boards exceed the size of the illuminated folios to protect them.
                              </decoNote>
                              <decoNote xml:id="b3" type="Cover" color="brown">
                                Full brown plain leather cover. On the front cover is stamped
                                the name of <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቤንት፡ ዩውል፡ የንሰን።</foreign> in gold characters.
                              </decoNote>
                              <decoNote xml:id="b4" type="SlipCase">
                                  The book is housed in a modern cardboard slipcase covered in green cloth, which folios the spine exposed.
                              </decoNote>
